{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"03fe7ba8e8","title":"同意所提战厚交换方针","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1dd93a0600","index":0,"year":1953,"month":3,"day":22,"articleId":"03fe7ba8e8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"1bdeb5780a","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"03fe7ba8e8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"谢明诺夫，即斯大林。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bda4d90f41","type":"title","text":"同意所提战厚交换方针！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"03fe7ba8e8"},{"id":"1bdeb5780a","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"03fe7ba8e8"},{"id":"e78a3698af","type":"paragraph","text":"三月二十日、二十一日两电均收到。我们同意所提方针。这实际上即是去年九月上句我们向谢明诺天同志所提三个方案中的一个方案，即将已达成协议的停房按比例交换，而将未达成协议的停房交给如印度一类的中立国管理待后解决。后来因美国在板门店采取横蛮态度，这个方案未能提出。现在提出这个方案是适合时机的。唯我方声明中应将仔房分为达成协议者和未达成协议者，而不称为愿回家者和不愿回家者，以免和我们历来反对所谓“自愿造返”原则相冲突。具体步骤待你回来的处","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"03fe7ba8e8"},{"id":"73ba90eed5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"03fe7ba8e8"},{"id":"32d3162ade","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五三年三月二十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"03fe7ba8e8"},{"id":"f7447bad44","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这是毛泽东给正在苏联访问的周思来的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"03fe7ba8e8"}],"page":{"id":"df4410ab65","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"03fe7ba8e8","start":89,"end":89}}}},"__N_SSG":true}